:
:  SYMBOL GENERATION MACRO
:
SYMGEN  MACRO(NAME) [
        IF      1-\SYMNAM
SYMNAM  EQ      .
SYM.NO  EQ      0
        EI
        SC      /NAME  /
SYAD|SYM.NO|    EQ      NAME
SYM.NO  EQ      SYM.NO+1
        ]
:
:  SYMBOL TABLE END
:
SYMEND  MACRO [
Q       EQ      0
SYMADR  WS      0
        RE      SYM.NO
        WC      SYAD|Q|
Q       EQ      Q+1
        ER
        WC      0       :TERMINATE LIST
        ]

        DS.CMD(SYM,DDTSYM)

DDTSYM
        LA      R2,SYMNAM               :POINT AT SYMBOL LIST
        LA      R3,SYMADR
DDTSY1
        L       R0,0,R3
        JE      DDTNOP                  :DONE
        SVC      OUT,CRLF
        LHI     R1,HEXZ.5
        SVC     KIO,$A10
        SVC     OUT,SPACE2
        SVC     OUT,0,R2
        LB      R0,0,R2
        AR      R2,R0
        AIS     R2,1
        AIS     R3,4
        J       DDTSY1

