:*****************************************************************
:
:	BINDEC IS A ROUTINE TO CONVERT INTERNAL BINARY REPRESENTATION OF
:	DATA TO ASCII DECIMAL CHARACTERS.
:
:	ARGUMENTS: R9 CONTAINS THE BINARY NUMBER
:	           R10 CONTAINS NUMBER OF DIGITS OF OUTPUT
